Facebook post by Noorie Noor Ananta, 8 November 2016. Photo of two hands holding peanuts/chana wrapped in Indian currency — one Rs 1000 note and one Rs 500 note used as disposable paper cones for snacks. Posted on the day of demonetization announcement. The now-worthless notes used as peanut wrappers = symbolic mockery of the demonetised currency. Aspect of Yug Parivartan: Divine Justice — the old system's currency reduced to waste paper.